                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A vasporan can molt specific parts of its skin to create sacs that catch wind currents or become filled with gases. In winds higher than a light wind, a vasporan\u2019s fly speed increases by 15 feet.",
