            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a reaction when hit by an attack that targets its KAC, a vasporan can molt its flesh to attempt to avoid the attack. The vasporan gains hardness 10 against the attack\u2019s damage and can take a guarded step. The vasporan can\u2019t use flash molt again for 1d4 rounds.",
